The last Olympic games were the 2020 Summer Olympics, which were held in Tokyo, Japan. However, due to the COVID-19 pandemic, the games were postponed and rescheduled to take place from July 23 to August 8, 2021. The games were officially referred to as the "2020 Summer Olympics" despite being held in 2021. The next Olympics, the 2022 Winter Olympics, will be held in Beijing, China, from February 4 to 20, 2022.